originalText.text: If you are looking for someone to love your dog as much as you love your own, Tribeca Dog Walking is the perfect choice. Tracy truly cares for animals and it shows in her work ethic. She is consistently reliable, detailed, and most of all, fun! Whenever my dog Dexter stays with her, they go on all kinds of adventures and he comes back a tired, happy pup! She is happy to keep you updated and posted with notes and texts and always makes herself available to you which I find really important.

originalText.text: I highly recommend Tribeca Dog Walking.  Tracy is very patient and made the extra effort to bond with our dog, who can be slow to get used to new people.  She clearly enjoys developing good relationships with the dogs she walks.  We appreciate the depth of experience she brings, her trustworthiness, and her positive approach.  Most important, our little guy has a great time with her.

originalText.text: We have had over 15 years of experience with tribeca pet services with our newfie and now two mini aussies. They provide us with excellent walking and boarding services. They are wonderful, caring, and i would not trust anyone else with our beloved doggies.

originalText.text: My dog, Maggie, LOVES Tracy! Whenever she sees her, she begins to cry in excitement. Tracy's love for dogs shines through the moment she meets them. Dogs are always happy around her. Tracy is a reliable, loving dog walker and dog sitter. Your dog will be happy to spend time with her when you are away. I highly recommend Tribeca Dog Walking.

originalText.text: I recommend Tribeca Dog Walking to anyone who needs caring, trustworthy, competent, and affordable dog walkers. They are absolutely the best around and a great new addition to NYC. The owner Tracy is an amazing "mom" to her own dog, Sammy, and by watching her interact with him, you know your dog will be in great hands with her.
